      <p class="lede">If any one of these is missing, the platform isn't white label local SEO — it's a rank tracker with a logo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-trend"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">1. Daily GBP execution.</h3>
        <p>Posts, photos, Q&A answers — all done by the platform. Not a checklist for your team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-dollar"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">2. Citations included.</h3>
        <p>60+ directory sync per client at the base price. Not a per-citation upcharge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-clock"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">3. Per-client brand voice.</h3>
        <p>Each client's replies sound like that client. Brand voice locked at onboarding.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-target"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">4. Branded reports.</h3>
        <p>Auto-PDF on the 1st of every month. Your logo. Your colors. Your email domain.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNIQUE SECTION: WHITE-LABEL VS THESTACC COMPARISON STRIP -->
