      <span class="label-pill">How agencies resell it</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">Brand the platform. <span class="accent">Bill your clients.</span></h2>
      <p class="lede">Set it up once. Add clients in 5 minutes each. Margins start the day you sign them.</p>
