          <p>Upload your logo, set your colors, point a subdomain. Clients see your brand from login to monthly report.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Custom domain (seo.youragency.com)</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Logo, colors, favicon</li>
