          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">02</span><span class="step-day">Per client · 5 minutes</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">Add a client. <span class="accent">First post in 24 hours.</span></h3>
          <p>One form per client: industry, location, brand voice, GBP access. theStacc starts posting the next morning. Map Pack rank movement within 30 days.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>5-min onboarding per client</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Brand voice locked at onboarding</li>
